Austria/Background.title: Background
Austria/Background.description: On May 13th 2024 PT Tiaramas Ronagemilang was invited by the Indonesian Department of Labor to attend a seminar introducing several talent agencies from Austria. The company has had experience in helping Indonesian workers specifically nurses and doctors find employment in Germany and so was very interested to see if it can expand its business.

Austria/List of Mangelberufe.title: List of Mangelberufe
Austria/List of Mangelberufe.description: What is considered to be Mangelberufe i.e. "professions in which shortage of labor exists" certainly change according to the situation in the labor market.

Austria/Migrating to Austria.title: Migrating to Austria
